title: Coast to Coast AM - Aug 19 2013 - Synchronicity & Enlightenm
description:
Date:	08-19-13
Host:	George Noory
Guests:	David Wilcock, Peter Cochrane
News segment guests: Mitch Battros, Lauren Weinstein

Hour 1: Co-founder of ConceptLabs, Peter Cochrane, gave an update on artificial intelligence and technology.

Hours 2, 3 & 4: Using history, astrology, and synchronicity theory, author and researcher David Wilcock discussed how there is a hidden architecture played out in cycles, guiding humanity toward enlightenment and spiritual progress.
